Please.

92
00:04:16.012 --> 00:04:17.788
Everybody calm down!

93
00:04:17.870 --> 00:04:20.090
Calm the fuck down!

94
00:04:26.613 --> 00:04:31.201
Please. you haven't done
anything yet you can't undo.

95
00:04:31.226 --> 00:04:33.707
