<i>♪ Que sera sera ♪</i>

137
00:07:25.792 --> 00:07:27.838
How much
further to town?

138
00:07:32.582 --> 00:07:34.646
It's too far. Over there!

139
00:07:34.671 --> 00:07:36.169
We can hide in
there till morning.

140
00:07:36.194 --> 00:07:37.681
Yeah.

141
00:07:37.706 --> 00:07:38.892
Okay.

142
00:07:41.807 --> 00:07:42.939
