until the morning.

254
00:14:36.135 --> 00:14:37.921
People used to do it
all the time here.

255
00:14:37.946 --> 00:14:39.501
They hid.

256
00:14:41.097 --> 00:14:42.663
That's how Sheriff
Boyd and his family

257
00:14:42.688 --> 00:14:44.468
